Package com.mlt.common.collections

Class Properties

java.lang.Object
com.mlt.common.collections.Properties
public class Properties
extends java.lang.Object
Properties backed by a hash map that seamlessly save/restore themselves to/from a JSON object. Note that in the getters no class validation is done, leaving the validation to a class cast exception.
